cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is about person re-identification using video sequences, which is a task related to computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach that involves attention mechanisms, which is a popular topic in machine learning and deep learning. Thus, cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves optimization of the feature extractor, which is a common task in artificial intelligence, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category. Finally, the paper involves distance matching, which is a common task in information retrieval, so cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category.
